{
  "stem": "24195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I-- some of the Russian soldiers were coming in and [? coming-- ?] you know, scowling through the basements and looking for women.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were pulling them out and raping them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got real angry about this in that building where we were, because there were a couple of young women.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they came over and they dragged them out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if they dragged them upstairs or I ran over to the-- there was a Russian command post had been set up in the next-- on the next street.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I ran over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I asked to see the commandant or whoever is in charge of the Russian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he had a-- he had a translator there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they don't speak Russian, but they had a translator.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said to me-- I told him about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, two of your men just come over and pulled some-- and dragged some women away, and they're probably raping them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he -- and that was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said-- or, officially not allowed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in order to pacify me, he says, well, I'm going to-- I'm going to send two of my like, MPs over there to straighten it out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came over, but from-- and they took them away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did take them away, but I don't think-- those two other soldiers away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't think anything happened to them there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had --the Russian soldiers had a victory celebration that lasted for eight days after Germany is surrounded, after they captured the city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they could do anything they wanted-- could loot anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They could do anything what they wanted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they could even shoot any civilian.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
